WEBVTT

06:24.550 --> 06:25.840 line:80%
The feast is about to start.

06:25.840 --> 06:26.990 line:80%
Stay and eat with us.

06:27.550 --> 06:28.210 line:80%
No, thanks.

06:29.070 --> 06:30.840 line:80%
My family just had a funeral,

06:31.360 --> 06:33.600 line:80%
and you didn't mind. Hiring me anyway

06:34.070 --> 06:35.600 line:80%
was already more than kind.
